 A Nigerian man simply identified  was caught trying to have sex with his close friend’s wife in Germany. A video on “EBALSBLOG” revealed that a business associate with his friend, got his wife’s number after he (aggrieved man) called him with her phone. The aggrieved man who expressed his disappointment over the incident stated that his friend who paid them a visit never embarked on the long journey to arrive in Bayern to see him but to sleep with his wife.